4$ km. We also discuss how future observations could\nconstrain the EOS and guide theoretical developments in nuclear physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jan 2018 21:28:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jun 2018 20:56:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
