h only a\nfew exceptions. Due to the uncertain contribution from other nucleosynthesis\nsites in ccSNe, such as neutrino winds or $\\alpha$-rich freeze out, we conclude\nthat the light p-nuclides 74$Se,78$Kr, 84Sr, and 92Mo may either still be\ncompletely or only partially produced in ccSNe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Jan 2018 22:14:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-09"}
